column5: I don't know if it was just us but for the past week the perch and bass in Kmepenfelt Bay have almost completely shut down its very strange because justa  couple of weeks ago they were biting pretty good, anyone have an idea why?

SAME THING ON SCUGOG!!! COUPLE WEEKS AGO WE WERE HITTIN LOTS OF FISH AND JUST YESTERDAY NOT 1 FISH!!! MNR GUY WAS AROUND AND SAID THE COLD FRONT MAY HAVE SHUT THEM DOWN AND PUSHED THEM INTO DEEPER WATERS!!
It's a Waning Gibbous moon, throw cool windy weather in and it's gonna be a tough bite
